<html><head><title>A design update from Shawn Lord</title></head><body class="newsbody" ><div class=newbody><h2>EverQuest Vault -- EQ </h3><h3>A design update from Shawn Lord</h3><p>The Lead Designer for EverQuest, Shawn Lord, has posted a new item over on EQLive which discusses the upcoming expansion, Omens of War.  Here's a clip.<br><blockquote><br>When I see all of the hard work that's being poured into the game  the Live changes; Epic creation; Omens content  right now, I can't help but be excited.  As developers, players, and as an industry, we're living in some of the most exciting times in gaming.  There are bound to be missteps, skeptical jaunts into the unknown, and thrilling victories for all of us.  It wouldn't be an adventure if there weren't.<br></blockquote><br>You can read the full update <a href="http://eqlive.station.sony.com/community/dev_view.jsp?id=62789">here</a>.</div><p><div classs=copyright><font face=arial size=2 color=#959595>News Story from EverQuest Vault -- EQ <br>News Date: Thursday, 8 July, 2004<br>Link: <a href="http://eqvault.ign.com/fullstory.php?id=168">http://eqvault.ign.com/fullstory.php?id=168</a><br>Printed On: Wed Sep 20 12:16:57 PDT 2006<br>©2005 IGN Entertainment</font></span>